title: Naoyuki Yamada
text:
is a Japanese <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="Vanraure%20Hachinohe">Vanraure Hachinohe</a>.
Playing career.
Naoyuki Yamada joined <a href="MIO%20Biwako%20Shiga">MIO Biwako Shiga</a> in 2010. In 2013, he moved to <a href="Blaublitz%20Akita">Blaublitz Akita</a>.
Club statistics.
"Updated to 26 December 2021".
